title: Leonard's new changes.
message:
Leonard's new changes.

* You can press button to take picture at any time

* You can say take picture at any time

* You can say any command at any time

* Checks for proper internet connection and if none is found it will do
3 beeps and allow 15 seconds for you to reconnect, otherwise will close
app

* You can apply all the filters you programmed, plus I added another 5
filters. I even included an option where you can say "Improve" and it
will automatically correct your image

* You can post to social media

* There are less bugs as initialization of TTS is controlled in a
better way

* Completed the lifecycles
